llboard'' Hot 100]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Top 100 Music Hits, Top 100 Music Charts, Top 100 Songs & The Hot 100: Best of 2008 |url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2008/hot-100-songs?begin=31&order=position |work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] |accessdate=2011-12-10}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|36\n|-\n|US [[Mainstream Top 40]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2008/pop-songs|title=Pop Songs \u2013 Year-End 2008|work=Billboard|accessdate=2019-09-12}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|39\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\" |Chart (2009)\n!scope=\"col\"|Position\n|-\n|[[\u00d63 Austria Top 40|Austrian Singles Chart]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Jahreshitparade 2009 \u2013 austriancharts.at |url=http://www.austriancharts.at/2009_single.asp |publisher=Hung Medien |language=German |accessdate=2010-07-23 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100910232559/http://www.austriancharts.at/2009_single.asp |archivedate=2010-09-10}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|5\n|-\n|[[Ultratop 50|Belgian Ultratop 50 (Flanders)]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/annual.asp?year=2009|title=ultratop.be \u2013 ULTRATOP BELGIAN CHARTS: Jaaroverzichten 2009 |publisher=ULTRATOP & Hung Medien / hitparade.ch |language=Dutch|accessdate=2010-07-23}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|19\n|-\n|[[Ultratop 50|Belgian Ultratop 40 (Wallonia)]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ultratop.be/fr/annual.asp?year=2009|title=ultratop.be \u2013 ULTRATOP BELGIAN CHARTS: Rapports Annuels 2009 |publisher=ULTRATOP & Hung Medien / hitparade.ch |language=French|accessdate=2010-07-23}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|6\n|-\n|[[Canadian Hot 100]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2009/canadian-hot-100?begin=11&order=position|title=Canadian Hot 100 Music Chart: Best of 2009 |accessdate=2010-07-23|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|11\n|-\n|[[