itle=FIMI \u2013 Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana \u2013 Ricerche e dati di mercato |publisher=Fimi.it |date=2010-01-19 |accessdate=2010-12-18 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100123194509/http://www.fimi.it/dett_ddmercato.php?id=47 |archivedate=2010-01-23}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|14\n|-\n|Romanian Top 100<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegrafonline.ro/1262901600/articol/search/108139/rockul_cenzurat_de_posturile_romanesti_de_radio.html |title=Rock-ul, cenzurat de posturile rom\u00e2ne\u015fti de radio |publisher=Telegraful |language=Romanian |accessdate=2009-01-10 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100211201846/http://www.telegrafonline.ro/1262901600/articol/search/108139/rockul_cenzurat_de_posturile_romanesti_de_radio.html |archivedate=2010-02-11}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|1\n|-\n| Russia Airplay ([[Tophit]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tophitru.com/airplay_year.shtml|title=Airplay Detection Tophit 200 Yearly \u2013 2009|publisher=[[Tophit]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100328204202/http://www.tophitru.com/airplay_year.shtml|archivedate=March 28, 2010|accessdate= 9 August 2019}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 40\n|-\n|[[Swiss Music Charts|Swiss Singles Chart]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Swiss Year-End Charts 2009 |url=http://www.swisscharts.com/year.asp?key=2009 |publisher=Hung Medien |accessdate=2010-07-23}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|4\n|-\n|[[UK Singles Chart]]<ref name=\"UK2009year\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ukchartsplus.co.uk/UKChartsPlusYE2009.pdf |title=Charts Plus Year end 2009 |publisher=Charts Plus |format=PDF |accessdate=2010-07-19}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|76\n|-\n|US [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2009/hot-100-songs|title= Top 100 Music Hits, Top 100 Music Charts, Top 100 Songs & The Hot 100: Best of 2009 |accessdate=2010-07-23|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|25\n|-\n|US [[Adult Contemporary]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2009/adult-contemporary-songs|title=Adult Contemporary Pop Songs \u2013 Year-End 2009|work=Billboard|accessdate=2019-09-12}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|17\n|-\n|US [[Adult Top 40]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2009/adult-pop-songs|title=Adult Pop Songs \u2013 Year-End 2009|work=Billboard|accessdate=2019-09-12}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|12\n|-\n|US [[Mainstream Top 40]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2009/pop-songs|title=Pop Songs \u2013 Year-End 2009|work=Billboard|accessdate=2019-09-12}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|35\n|}\n\n===All-time charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\" |Chart (1958-2018)\n!scope=\"col\"|Position\n|-\n|US [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/hot-100-60th-anniversary|title=Billboard Hot 100 60th Anniversary| date=August 31, 2018 |work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] }}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|525\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Certifications==\n{{Certification Table Top}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Australia|title=Hot n Cold|artist=Katy Perry|certyear=2013|type=single|award=Platinum|number=5|accessdate=10 March 2012}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Austria|title=Hot n Cold|artist=Katy Perry|certyear=2008|relyear=2008|type=single|award=Platinum|accessdate=10 March 2012}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Belgium|title=Hot n Cold|artist=Katy Perry|certyear=2009|relyear=2008|relmonth=9|type=single|award=Gold|accessdate=10 March 2012}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Brazil|title=Hot n Cold|artist=Katy Perry|certyear=2008|relyear=2008|type=single|award=Platinum|accessdate=10 March 2012}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Canada|title=Hot n Cold|artist=Katy Perry|relyear=2008|relmonth=2|certyear=