00|''Billboard'' Hot 100]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2009/hot-100-songs|title= Top 100 Music Hits, Top 100 Music Charts, Top 100 Songs & The Hot 100: Best of 2009 |accessdate=2010-07-23|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|25\n|-\n|US [[Adult Contemporary]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2009/adult-contemporary-songs|title=Adult Contemporary Pop Songs \u2013 Year-End 2009|work=Billboard|accessdate=2019-09-12}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|17\n|-\n|US [[Adult Top 40]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2009/adult-pop-songs|title=Adult Pop Songs \u2013 Year-End 2009|work=Billboard|accessdate=2019-09-12}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|12\n|-\n|US [[Mainstream Top 40]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2009/pop-songs|title=Pop Songs \u2013 Year-End 2009|work=Billboard|accessdate=2019-09-12}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|35\n|}\n\n===All-time charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\" |Chart (1958-2018)\n!scope=\"col\"|Position\n|-\n|US [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/hot-100-60th-anniversary|title=Billboard Hot 100 60th Anniversary| date=August 31, 2018 |work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] }}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|525\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Certifications==\n{{Certification Table Top}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Australia|title=Hot n Cold|artist=Katy Perry|certyear=2013|type=single|award=Platinum|number=5|accessdate=10 March 2012}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Austria|title=Hot n Cold|artist=Katy Perry|certyear=2008|relyear=2008|type=single|award=Platinum|accessdate=10 March 2012}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Belgium|title=Hot n Cold|artist=Katy Perry|certyear=2009|relyear=2008|relmonth=9|type=single|award=Gold|accessdate=10 March 2012}}\n{{Certification Table En